Nicole, 5; Thomas, 4; James 3; Robert, 1{; and Michael, 5 months,
Wade said.
   Mrs. Ireland's husband, Thomas, 33, was at work when the fire
broke out about 10 a.m., and the couple's only surviving child,
Jamie, 7, was in school, Wade said.
   The cause of the fire was under investigation, but foul play was
not suspected, Wade said.
