<HEAD>First Boeing 747-400 Christened for European Market</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By DAVID LAWRENCE</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>EVERETT, Wash. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The first of the new Boeing 747-400 jumbo
